<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.1.7">
<l>ammā ṉāḻippirā ṉavaṉevviṭat tāṉyāṉā</l>
<l>remmā pāviyarkkumvitivāykkiṉṟu vāykkuṅkaṇṭīr</l>
<l>kaimmā tuṉpoḻittā yeṉṟukaitalai pūcaliṭṭē</l>
<l>meymmā lāyoḻintēṉempirāṉumeṉ mēlāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The father, the discus lord, in which place is he? Who am I?</l>
<l>The fate of however great a sinner has succeeded. [Mine] succeeds, see!</l>
<l>Wailing loudly with hands [and] head “o you who ended the misery of the trunk animal”</l>
<l>I ended up with Māl being the truth. And our lord is above me.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
